@ variables are not case sensitive

@CLIPBOARD	Set by the product filter addon and used elsewhere in the jelly file
@HOMEPAGE	Only exists if is a home page in ContentBlock.
		Set by the db jellyword during preprocess.
		Hardcoded specifically to reads of 'ContentBlock' and dependant on the field 'home' whether it is set or not
		Designed to be used in conjunction with condition=@HOMEPAGE but can be used elsewhere
